				\begin{document}$$HD = 0$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M50"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>H</mml:mi><mml:mi>D</mml:mi><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mn>0</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12859_2020_3775_Article_IEq22.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>, else they are in conflict. In other words, when <inline-formula id="IEq23"><alternatives><tex-math id="M51">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
