      <p id="Par54">In order to evaluate the quality of the obtained haplotypes, reconstruction rate (RR) [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR38">38</xref>] and MEC score are two useful measurements. Let <inline-formula id="IEq25"><alternatives><tex-math id="M55">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
